Create .pot files with xgettext:
xgettext -Lperl -d dss-addon -k_ --omit-header *.js

Translate them to json objects with po2json (http://jsgettext.berlios.de/)
echo -n 'var locale_data={"dss-addon":' > dss-addon.js
po2json -p dss-addon.po >> dss-addon.js
echo "};" >> dss-addon.js

Live example for copy-paste usage:

echo -n 'var framework_locale_data=' > de_DE/LC_MESSAGES/dss-addon-framework.js; po2json -p de_DE/dss-addon-framework.po >> de_DE/LC_MESSAGES/dss-addon-framework.js; echo -n ';' >> de_DE/LC_MESSAGES/dss-addon-framework.js;

echo -n 'var locale_data=' > de_DE/LC_MESSAGES/dss-addon.js; po2json -p de_DE/dss-addon.po >> de_DE/LC_MESSAGES/dss-addon.js; echo -n ';' >> de_DE/LC_MESSAGES/dss-addon.js;
